text.tspan: Clicksiege is a battle for territory among three rival clans.
You will join one of these class and battle from either your
smartphone or the central battle station.
On your smartphone, join the battle at clicksiege.com and
move into the territory you want to battle in. Hold majority
control with your clanmates to claim the territory. Claim
all four territories and your clan will win!

At the battlestation, choose the territory you want to attack
with the switch and then click like crazy! Keep an eye out
for clanmates who need help in their territory to help them
